Effect the necessary adjusting entries, if any, to correct the special trust fund balance of DRRMF for CY 2018;



Instruct the Municipal Accountant to effect the following adjusting entry:



Submit to the Audit Team the necessary Notes to Financial Statements for LDRRMF for CY 2019 in the format prescribed by Annex D of COA Circular 2012-002.

